@SkyRoutePlatform.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5118

### Search Flights Test
POST {{SkyRoutePlatform.API_HostAddress}}/api/flights/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "originCode": "JFK",
  "destinationCode": "LHR",
  "departureDate": "2026-08-15",
  "passengers": 2,
  "cabinClass": "Economy"
}

###

### Create Booking Test
POST {{SkyRoutePlatform.API_HostAddress}}/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "flightId": "GA-101-20260815",
  "cabinClass": "Economy",
  "passengers": 2,
  "fullName": "Alex Carter",
  "email": "alex.carter@example.com",
  "documentType": "PassportNumber",
  "documentNumber": "X12345678"
}

